id: pm-zpa5
title: Add pm plan list subcommand or did-you-mean to pm list --type Plan
description: `pm plan list` produces a generic unknown subcommand error. Agents naturally try this. Either add `list` to plan subcommand enum (route to `pm list --type Plan`) or surface a did-you-mean hint pointing to `pm list --type Plan`. Lowers retry tokens.
